Package planning.actions

Class ActionParserHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • planning.actions.ActionParserHelper
  • public class ActionParserHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is made to identify the type of action easily. Why this exists: So that the code to parse the type of action isn't repeated frequently.

    • Method Detail

      • GetActionType

        public static ActionParserHelper.ActionEnum GetActionType​(burlap.mdp.core.action.Action theAction)
        Gets an enumerator representing the action type from the Actions module. Why this exists: To simplify action decoding for use in the bot. How this works: Looks at the action's name up to the first '_' and then matches that to the types.
        Parameters:
        theAction - any Action object. Expected to be one of the ones from the Actions module.
        Returns:
        an ActionEnum indicating the action type. Defaults to UNKNOWN if the action does not match any others.
